title: I'm not in the club I made after the clubs outage
body: Bruh, I'm not in the club I made anymore and everyone in the club is still in it....

replies.body: This is a visual issue that we're aware of and are working on a fix. I can't provide an ETA on when that fix will deploy, but check in on [this post](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/nMisJPK8-clubs-outage-oct-2016) for any further updates on this.
Check the board before posting man! Tonnes of people with this issue.
